# Phase 2: Election & Position Management

Build full CRUD for elections and their positions.

## Proposed Changes

### Server Actions

#### [NEW] [elections.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/elections.ts)

Server actions for elections:
- `getElections()` — List all elections with position count
- `createElection(formData)` — Create with name, validates non-empty
- `updateElection(formData)` — Update name
- `toggleElection(id)` — Toggle `isActive` (only one election active at a time — deactivates others)
- `deleteElection(id)` — Delete with cascade (positions + candidates via schema)

#### [NEW] [positions.ts](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/actions/positions.ts)

Server actions for positions within an election:
- `getPositions(electionId)` — List positions ordered by `order`
- `createPosition(formData)` — Create with name, order, maxVotes, electionId
- `updatePosition(formData)` — Update name, order, maxVotes
- `deletePosition(id)` — Delete (cascades candidates via schema)

---

### Election List Page

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/app/dashboard/elections/page.tsx)

Replace placeholder with full election management:
- Table showing elections (name, status badge, position count, created date)
- "Create Election" button → dialog with name input
- Row actions: Edit name, Toggle active/inactive, Delete (with confirmation)
- Click an election row → navigates to detail page

---

### Election Detail Page (Position Management)

#### [NEW] [page.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/sja-voting/app/dashboard/elections/[id]/page.tsx)

Election detail with inline position management:
- Header showing election name + status
- Table of positions (name, order, max votes, candidate count)
- "Add Position" button → dialog with name, order, maxVotes fields
- Row actions: Edit, Delete (with confirmation)
- Back link to election list

---

### UI Components Needed

#### ShadCN components to add (via `bunx shadcn add`):
- `dialog` — for create/edit modals
- `table` — for data tables
- `badge` — for status badges
- `dropdown-menu` — for row action menus
- `select` — for maxVotes selector

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Navigate to `/dashboard/elections` — see empty state
2. Create an election → appears in table
3. Toggle election active → badge updates, other elections deactivate
4. Click election → navigate to detail page
5. Add positions with name/order/maxVotes → appear in table
6. Edit and delete positions → table updates
7. Delete election → redirects to list, cascade removes positions
